tead of writing a scenario, feel free to comment on the story below.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tThe manager had a charming personality and gave professional responses, with just the right amount of humor, a likeable character. Both the reporter and the intern were writing down notes along the way, the intern being the keener and more enthusiastic one and Wolfe only wrote down a few points here and there. In case they missed anything as well as for future reference, the entire conversation was recorded on audio. Wolfe had the courtesy to ask the interviewee for permission to record prior to the start of the interview.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/167730661900/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a></p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p787936/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p787936\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p790562/\">沪江“每日一说”功能开通！口语就该这么练！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p789945/\">卡梅伦辞职演讲双语全文 附语言点精析</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p790750/\">玩大了！英国脱欧 英语或被踢出欧盟官方语言</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p788294/\">一天之计在于晨：三件小事让你做个晨型人</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p790664/\">囧研究：再熄灯睡前玩手机 你就等着瞎吧！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p789832/\">吉祥物被杀运动员被抢 巴西奥运目测笑掉大牙</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p790765/\">脱欧Brexit悔脱Regrexit 公投后新单词真多</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a